{"tid":1333363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由今日起「建制派」要改稱「權貴派」","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:53:57.000Z","uid":54303,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a64ef34a06fa7e33a61c12906b74292febbdec0d","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"點評時下局勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n受呢位巴打既post啟發<br />\n佢成篇文都好高質 <br />\n有一點我覺得尤其重要而值得特別講<br />\n就係要幫「權貴派」正名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿 自由黨唔洗講啦<br />\n民建聯扮到好關心民生 <br />\n實際上咪又係利益輸送既仆街<br />\n成日支持起大白象 同以各種名目攞政府funding<br />\n其實蛇齋餅糭比起佢地貪番黎既錢<br />\n簡直係微不足道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫佢地做「權貴派」有咩好處呢？<br />\n第一係分化 我地要令民建聯果班窮撚支持者猶豫<br />\n覺得自己冇被充分代表<br />\n第二係政治啟蒙 因為當市民接受左呢個名 就自自然然會想知民建聯點樣「親權貴」<br />\n慢慢就會知道有幾多賣港議案通過左<br />\n第三 我地改口無成本架！<br />\n而當我地日日講 選舉講 不停講<br />\n佢地「權貴派」要花好多資源去做形象工程<br />\n（咁當然非權貴派都要努力宣傳同做地區工作啦）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊講<br />\n屌你老母奶共權貴派！唔要送中！立即普選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d242512aafe70ef59048de75254d7ac9ada8e081","tid":1333363,"uid":202876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好search 民建聯 陳恆鑌 打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e845f4f2b748b516d7821757581652efd2fefd2b","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"咁改口對於而家局勢有冇幫助？有！<br />\n改稱「權貴派」可以：<br />\n1. 減弱敵方政治動員能力<br />\n2. 增加我方正當性<br />\n3. 鼓勵一般市民去連儂牆吸收訊息 有利遍地開花"},{"pid":"1d2f0540f75c0f064784168f669b6b5ef72fcbb0","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d242512aafe70ef59048de75254d7ac9ada8e081","tid":1333363,"uid":202876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好search 民建聯 陳恆鑌 打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"要不停貼民建聯賣港實錄<br />\n而家社會對政治關注度高 係時候反洗腦"},{"pid":"ef2031861bdb078a38a0278afa91278ae05e8e66","tid":1333363,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"藝正權"},{"pid":"a510468f733788d68799ad30a33bde72474564a7","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5dfea56a18f162e7744100e46eb3ac13997680","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541b8395263923d56f7f1188426b52fca9cfbac5","tid":1333363,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"f0a89a16280b3b2a200e7435eae14e4d5daa6757","tid":1333363,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"之前都有人講過 親中派/北京派"},{"pid":"8a79fe02f7a0bb945e309a632c49a064aebf240b","tid":1333363,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"港共"},{"pid":"73e7be280f2bc99b6907ec56b8dda54987b5e8d0","tid":1333363,"uid":270533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"權貴派，好! 其實現在發展落去真係好似階級鬥爭，有少少唔同嘅就係有一班明事理嘅中產都嘅係抗爭者呢邊。"},{"pid":"222a3d504048b20a63926fa9387435c8a606b3d7","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0a89a16280b3b2a200e7435eae14e4d5daa6757","tid":1333363,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"之前都有人講過 親中派/北京派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"親中無咁好<br />\n因為香港仲有班大中華膠係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有要分化窮撚藍絲 權貴派比較好"},{"pid":"eb39c3a1118d48e91a62fa87a96b8d87e5847e44","tid":1333363,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"文宣要出手"},{"pid":"91b5181aa611f09366efa16c501fb551d1c1240b","tid":1333363,"uid":38177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:50.000Z","msg":"權貴依個詞簡單易明，一絕"},{"pid":"73d65248811d0a02652d3ca95a13826f3b93982c","tid":1333363,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"獨裁派"},{"pid":"46e06df05e55991b7ba390c7e8b6a8ad31868313","tid":1333363,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"文宣隊出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d6390ab08a8c6a3682ca1da00217058e6ba3a6","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfbe64380a4ef5a1dcd58f2cdc65f72206e6a83","tid":1333363,"uid":129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:12:56.000Z","msg":"但如果有上層社會o既人係支持民主<br />\n咁佢地又係屬於權貴派？<br />\n我地玩階級鬥爭其實係玩埋自己<br />\n因為我地唔係當權者"},{"pid":"8ff354bb599e8582af99444159c2e43b8db62f32","tid":1333363,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"賣港派 最直線啦"},{"pid":"33a01086d5dff66bb487b1a31f9b72f7b5c7405e","tid":1333363,