603b0b5bee","tid":1333363,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"拎返晒啲民建聯收中聯辦收共產黨嘅證據出嚟搞大佢啦<br />\n啲乜鳩字畫捐一千萬呀，黨慶獻唱一曲一齊食飯之類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9988fe737ff0bb069c819d9fb58e12f0dcb6d0d8","tid":1333363,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:28:02.000Z","msg":"推 權貴派 721"},{"pid":"0aa88d87cbee26b309bb0dccc5e8d654249d30ce","tid":1333363,"uid":270763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1e9f9ba68e6293367552c64b3d3fe09b674e4da","tid":1333363,"uid":250048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"貼佢地外國國籍，話佢地先係「真外國勢力」有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c92c63d576579a9830fcd16af1786215f47fea3","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eae19ecc8bf280f4efcaf923686d63c507034cc","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e9f9ba68e6293367552c64b3d3fe09b674e4da","tid":1333363,"uid":250048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"貼佢地外國國籍，話佢地先係「真外國勢力」有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:32:34.000Z","msg":"一定有啦 好多藍絲都唔知<br />\n權貴派議員先最唔愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3265dba73b59d2bbb88eeb389319bf168b704","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f124cbfb98d2183acb96d24730ab4536ed19b8","tid":1333363,"uid":247690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:42:22.000Z","msg":"係要講開我講多句。<br />\n<br />\n而家的泛民，同以後所以入議會的黃絲，全部應該歸類成「建制派」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地為左入立法會，全部都發左支持國家的誓言。所有事都要跟足規距玩，無左在野抗爭果種自由同埋任玩野任講野。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話佢地投敵，但隨往新的抗爭者進入議會「泛民」已經唔足以區分佢地。而本土派、港獨派呢種名詞，一講就領野。<br />\n方便區分都好，我地要想一套新的分類方式，黎應付變化極大的社運形勢。<br />\n<br />\n我提議就咁的。<br />\n泛民、入議會的兄弟，統一稱做建制派或者新建制派。<br />\n勇武、本土、港獨派。可以叫做「在野民主派」、「在野反對派」。<br />\n<br />\n原來的建制，可以用PO主講的權貴派。<br />\n李偲嫣呢種，...一時想唔好..."},{"pid":"92355fc743f48cd934e5e6c2b9f7670c3f625c27","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aa548af653d9866f5816ab73d35959663515d8","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1260ce48d6eceb5859824e206a74f606dec7965b","tid":1333363,"uid":283395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贊成<br />\n權貴派！"},{"pid":"12006b47ee6ffdb076a938553e763f84b62721d0","tid":1333363,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:49:16.000Z","msg":"保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0526b9853b1e3da2048fe22611a0469a87e2a052","tid":1333363,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"如果標籤佢地係權貴派<br />\n總有藍絲沖出嚟話公民黨一類精英，都係服務權貴<br />\n而工聯會呢又會狡辯話自己係服務工人階級云云<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n會唔會用「維穩派」好啲呢？<br />\n佢哋唔可以話自己反對維穩"},{"pid":"fc70bd064a4cf4c53baa0cfdfa6373f45678778e","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0526b9853b1e3da2048fe22611a0469a87e2a052","tid":1333363,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"如果標籤佢地係權貴派<br />\n總有藍絲沖出嚟話公民黨一類精英，都係服務權貴<br />\n而工聯會呢又會狡辯話自己係服務工人階級云云<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n會唔會用「維穩派」好啲呢？<br />\n佢哋唔可以話自己反對維穩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"你會挑動愛國藍絲神經<br />\n改口既主要目的係分化同負面宣傳<br />\n事實係點唔重要"},{"pid":"792ede3fb018c717ce045ca4c03a3906f3a300ff","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408f5d7322c6d90ea5115fce4ece6f2e331c0f2f","tid":1333363,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a5c8481b94da75a280f2a6fea5c1764d161ce4","tid":1333363,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b8cab451f58b07ff94b4399f5589997a8d01571","tid":1333363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbfbe64380a4ef5a1dcd58f2cdc65f72206e6a83","tid":1333363,"uid":129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:12:56.000Z","msg":"但如果有上層社會o既人係支持民主<br />\n咁佢地又係屬於權貴派？<br />\n我地玩階級鬥爭其實係玩埋自己<br />\n因為我地唔係當權者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以舉個例 講下邊個有錢佬唔係自私同奶共？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"田少嗰啲平時奶共<br />\n但有重大爭議都會睇遊行人數站邊<br />\n呢啲係人民有能力影響到的權貴派<br />\n重要時刻可以拉攏下<br />\n同只聽命西環的機械人唔同<br />\n<br />\n其實建制派唔係鐵板一塊<br />\n所以我覺得應該就住建制唔同板塊去label佢地<br />\n亦可達到分化作用"},{"pid":"6c68f5b68aa7c9e281b11962d4a93c8e62ca8e5d","tid":1333363,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:04:09.000Z",